description: This file defines a React functional component named EmptyState, which displays a placeholder UI when no notes are available. It includes UI elements such as an icon, title, description, and a button that triggers a callback function to create a new note.

methods.name: EmptyState({ onNew })
methods.description: A React functional component that renders an empty state UI with an icon, title, description, and a button to create a new note. Receives 'onNew' as a prop to handle the creation action.
